Cosatu May Recommend State-Owned Construction Company

-- B y   B r i a n   L a t h a m
-- 
2011-06-30T14:59:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-30/cosatu-may-recommend-state-owned-construction-company.html
The Congress of South African Trade
Unions, the country’s biggest labor union federation, may
recommend that the government form a state-owned construction
company for infrastructure programs,  Zwelinzima Vavi , the
organization’s general secretary, said.  Cosatu is in an alliance with the the  South African
Communist Party  and  South Africa ’s ruling African National
Congress party. Vavi spoke at a Cosatu congress in Midrand,
South Africa today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Latham in Johannesburg at at   blatham@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at   asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 